<|asst|>
Currently, I don't have direct access to population data specific to ZIP codes or even broader regions like cities directly linked with their ZIP codes from within my available tools. However, you can typically find this information through various public and governmental data sources such as U.S. Census Bureau data or city planning websites. These sources often provide detailed demographic reports that include population numbers, which can be searched by ZIP code or city name.

