<|asst|>
[Language Segmenter(chinese="\u4eca\u5929\u662f2024\u5e744\u670825\u65e5\uff0c\u661f\u671f\u56db\u3002")]
<|end|>
<|tool|>
[{"name": "Language Segmenter", "results": {"segments": ["今天是2024年4月25日", "星期四"]}}]
<|end|>
<|asst|>
[Classify(text="\u4eca\u5929\u662f2024\u5e744\u670825\u65e5")]
<|end|>
<|tool|>
[{"name": "Classify", "results": {"classification": "Dates and Events", "confidence_score": 0.92}}]
<|end|>
<|asst|>
[Classify(text="\u661f\u671f\u56db")]
<|end|>
<|tool|>
[{"name": "Classify", "results": {"classification": "Lifestyle & Hobbies", "confidence_score": 0.87}}]
<|end|>
<|asst|>
The first segment "今天是2024年4月25日" has been categorized as "Dates and Events" with a confidence score of 0.92. The second segment "星期四" falls under "Lifestyle & Hobbies" with a confidence score of 0.87. This analysis should help in compiling your social media report.
<|end|>


