I am analyzing a dataset named 'customer_segments' to understand customer patterns better. Please perform a K-Means clustering with 5 clusters using the 'k-means++' initialization method. After that, I would like to use the cluster centers from this analysis as input for DBSCAN clustering with a radius of 0.5 and a minimum of 10 samples required per cluster.
