I just started playing this new VR game and I'm struggling with the difficulty. I'd also like to customize the environment to be more immersive for my evening gaming sessions. The game id is "VRQuest100". Can you set the difficulty to "Medium", adjust the environment for evening play, and check if there's an optimal time for me to play based on my past performances?
